{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"37230-tall-and-short","title":"Tall and Short","description":"Can you tell which family members are tall and which are short? This book demonstrates the concept of opposites— tall and short— through the members of a child’s family. ","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Celia  Bolam"],"illustrators":["Seat Sopheap"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/37230-tall-and-short"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101345/size3/e64bf7a17d2acc3605b1e60a19301d27.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/101345/size6/e64bf7a17d2acc3605b1e60a19301d27.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70749/size6/46a409cb5f7687ce9fb564c2f5f8f6f8.jpg","text":"Pa is getting my hat.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70750/size6/074d1c6167f8db09889882b6c820489e.jpg","text":"Pa is tall.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70751/size6/9b86de0e05551703824d2ec821c9904a.jpg","text":"Ma is getting my shirt.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70752/size6/1e7662e721f3cc16c95533711748eda5.jpg","text":"Pa is taller than Ma.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/70753/size6/96e501e2a9dc16a951c9dedaffe65944.jpg","text":"My sister is getting my book.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_cr